title: Growing Our Generation: Advocate, farmer, mother, business woman (Ohio Chamber of Commerce)
text: ( Source : Ohio Chamber of Commerce ) Hello ! My name is Kristin Reese and I live on a small farm in Baltimore in Fairfield County . I am a mom to two little farmers: Campbell who is 8 and Parker who is 6. I work as a Realtor for HER Realtors ,
